{"tid":744122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國呢隊西波都幾撚賤","createTime":"2018-07-15T18:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T18:40:30.000Z","uid":34256,"like":33,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62b6dab6762eed49b94e98ce285819f3e8428b4c","tid":744122,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"格仔唔想咁早送人返屋企<br />\n場場同人打足120分鐘 仲射埋12碼先走<br />\n比對面隊可以留係鏡頭前多一陣 <br />\n仲要場場都讓人一粒先 盡顯君子風度<br />\n反觀法國成日90分鐘就收人皮<br />\n快快脆趕收工咁:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n球王美斯可能最後一屆都唔比面 <br />\n呀蘇又比佢地射走埋<br />\n呢場仲要入左4粒 一啲面子都唔比<br />\n落機鋪打機都識讓round啦法國班生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好在個龍識做派返粒比格仔等佢地輸得冇咁醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n法國好應該開波前跑返90分鐘囉（格仔3場120<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n咁樣贏冠軍 我真係唔會認同lor唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/croatia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cfa8bf46fe947e947a355ae7b506c260120cae","tid":744122,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/croatia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/croatia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60fb20bafd8e3acb85ab2f6630fcf17b7d81410","tid":744122,"uid":167777,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"😍😍樓豬好撚型牙 唔盲目追隨強隊"},{"pid":"932fd7680bc96a484fdc441925b054a184e1d01c","tid":744122,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b60fb20bafd8e3acb85ab2f6630fcf17b7d81410","tid":744122,"uid":167777,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"😍😍樓豬好撚型牙 唔盲目追隨強隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"洗乜講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/croatia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b902e3eccf479895db0fbd5bce0b7f0